Parents asked. And so here is our first ever Long Beach Moms 2022 Summer Camp Guide!

We are thrilled to showcase our partner’s camps who offer summer activities this coming summer!

We have selections from babes aged 4 - 18+, and there's an assortment to choose from to get the wiggles out, stretch the tech brain, and to learn new skills!

